{"tid":376530,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有個post話qb剪頭髮好差叫人考牌，真係笑出聲","createTime":"2017-08-27T05:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T10:43:11.000Z","uid":110080,"like":106,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4cce1176c11f531133481eee1e6838653e46e1c","tid":376530,"uid":110080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"去得qb剪既人根本就對自己既髮型無要求<br />\n<br />\n睇死你現實都係柒頭一個<br />\n<br />\n但凡對自己有小小要求既人都會搵一間好既髮型鋪長期跟黎剪<br />\n<br />\n又話咩貴貴貴 大佬呀 旺角大把200內既選擇啦<br />\n<br />\n自己區就要靠自己發掘下<br />\n<br />\n一二百都嫌貴果d就抵你成世做柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：自己區剪開二百幾"},{"pid":"50cd9bcd0d5b8df9df0254342538bad21c161bdb","tid":376530,"uid":3122,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"咪教佢做人啦"},{"pid":"540d4ac302cdd81170a4207ea01a97fcd4674d11","tid":376530,"uid":22507,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"問題係幾百蚊剪完都係差"},{"pid":"d445f4b392156d491d0326e9be4801e4a17ca943","tid":376530,"uid":36035,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc1df0f766da65f16350ae8ef4a38e82c265e32f","tid":376530,"uid":110080,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問題係幾百蚊剪完都係差</blockquote><br />\n樣衰點剪都係差架啦，劉華江華方中信吳彥祖都係短髮，唔覺髮型有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續為自己既柒搵藉口<br />\n根本好多人個樣都正正常常<br />\n但就係衰在剪左個柒頭 <br />\n<br />\n係 本身柒既人剪完靚頭都係柒 但至少無咁柒<br />\n起碼比人感覺好少少<br />\n咁已經好難得 <br />\n<br />\n你鐘意為自己柒搵藉口就無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b97c873ffa1871a01993db2d795217bfb33972","tid":376530,"uid":110080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問題係幾百蚊剪完都係差</blockquote><br />\n要試多d 呢間唔得就下一間 實有間岩你<br />\n想剪得靚緊係要比d心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd21ec125a71ae624b11f1ea0a66525790cd21f","tid":376530,"uid":62289,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n唔肯付出又要最好既野"},{"pid":"9bc0a249d5e45fda58383b2cfe8af70f01720c14","tid":376530,"uid":80633,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"剪過好多間二百左右洗剪，大部分都係中伏，頭髮又生得快，三個月要剪兩次，qb根本係最佳選擇，行街番工中間抽到半個鐘出來就邊度都有得剪<br />\n我柒唔柒我無咩資格講，但我又真係想睇下你個頭又有乜咁令你自豪"},{"pid":"b035e1eb8bb800d14b161cb3f2477a8ecb95ddf6","tid":376530,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剪過好多間二百左右洗剪，大部分都係中伏，頭髮又生得快，三個月要剪兩次，qb根本係最佳選擇，行街番工中間抽到半個鐘出來就邊度都有得剪<br />\n我柒唔柒我無咩資格講，但我又真係想睇下你個頭又有乜咁令你自豪</blockquote><br />\n問題係你啲毒撚fd話qb差喎"},{"pid":"53bde5785f1de28611c6aec6a4194baaf16f6912","tid":376530,"uid":129644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剪過好多間二百左右洗剪，大部分都係中伏，頭髮又生得快，三個月要剪兩次，qb根本係最佳選擇，行街番工中間抽到半個鐘出來就邊度都有得剪<br />\n我柒唔柒我無咩資格講，但我又真係想睇下你個頭又有乜咁令你自豪</blockquote><br />\n問題係你啲毒撚fd話qb差喎</blockquote><br />\n接受到柒既咪繼續剪qb <br />\n但佢地又要鬧wo衣家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於我個頭就正正常常 無比人話過柒lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4087c037810a0fc8e492d1c0b087ff7ae94083c4","tid":376530,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31375ed80c2f6d65aae6f5a1503174ceb8638f9f","tid":376530,"uid":20563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"去QB 屌QB 剪得差，就好似搭廉航屌廉航delay 賠得少"},{"pid":"72015b50fe7396c3cc899369581d9068138812b8","tid":376530,"uid":80633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剪過好多間二百左右洗剪，大部分都係中伏，頭髮又生得快，三個月要剪兩次，qb根本係最佳選擇，行街番工中間抽到半個鐘出來就邊度都有得剪<br />\n我柒唔柒我無咩資格講，但我又真係想睇下你個頭又有乜咁令你自豪</blockquote><br />\n問題係你啲毒撚fd話qb差喎</blockquote><br />\n咁就係毒撚fd問題啦"},{"pid":"5a28e3231f82d6b8164f3e4cf069932b19f8c306","tid":376530,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"根本唔關髮型事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409eebd09003c69f5763d7163dad4a050c932ade","tid":376530,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"幫趁 qb 通常都係對品質冇要求，剪髮過一舊覺得唔值咁貴，或 salon 恐懼症候群，而做得 qb 既多數一係 salon 既冇客底 stylist，做七八年都升唔到 stylist，或做下停下唔知自已做既乜既 part time 精。"},{"pid":"5a690961672a57a33c70519022683b298f36213a","tid":376530,"uid":55445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"Your face your fate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e98363743ffcef69192acace5fab99e9f3a95af","tid":376530,"uid":18977,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:14:01.000Z","msg":"剪速剪根本係毒撚先會做嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入嚟就係為睇毒撚駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2de547d1b31dade5c39ecdeaf119dfad0425fec","tid":376530,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:14:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9d91760c462bdb7d40261a54c4f8cae64fc72996","tid":376530,"uid":25050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T20:25:15.000Z","msg":"咪幫毒撚轉形啦"},{"pid":"7cbbb150d498ccde456d3ea6c86b29a1b665c008","tid":376530,"uid":53145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"我唔排除有d qb質素真係好差劣 但係話qb剪得差大部分應該樣既問題 我剪qb返工一樣有人讚剪得好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src