":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>問題係幾百蚊剪完都係差</blockquote><br />\n樣衰點剪都係差架啦，劉華江華方中信吳彥祖都係短髮，唔覺髮型有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人成撚日用呢啲來做例子，on99. 佢哋短頭髮係因為短頭髮適合佢哋，關佢哋個樣靚唔靚咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果佢哋剪留陰嘅頭，電攣毛，undercut ,米又係7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本只係佢個髮型適合佢哋，人人如果剪到一個適合自己嘅髮型，個觀感都會好好多"},{"pid":"1a5e91477aab8718d416c6b8774fb0be08139df9","tid":376530,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問題係幾百蚊剪完都係差</blockquote><br />\n樣衰點剪都係差架啦，劉華江華方中信吳彥祖都係短髮，唔覺髮型有咩特別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續為自己既柒搵藉口<br />\n根本好多人個樣都正正常常<br />\n但就係衰在剪左個柒頭 <br />\n<br />\n係 本身柒既人剪完靚頭都係柒 但至少無咁柒<br />\n起碼比人感覺好少少<br />\n咁已經好難得 <br />\n<br />\n你鐘意為自己柒搵藉口就無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港好多男仔都係樣衰"},{"pid":"ef2331e137a5d8889a53debeebd10bb31c77bf0f","tid":376530,"uid":17211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剪過好多間二百左右洗剪，大部分都係中伏，頭髮又生得快，三個月要剪兩次，qb根本係最佳選擇，行街番工中間抽到半個鐘出來就邊度都有得剪<br />\n我柒唔柒我無咩資格講，但我又真係想睇下你個頭又有乜咁令你自豪</blockquote><br />\n三個月剪兩次有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048653ac16a2baa7b4cc514d8faf6ba3896ddf06","tid":376530,"uid":41604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剪過好多間二百左右洗剪，大部分都係中伏，頭髮又生得快，三個月要剪兩次，qb根本係最佳選擇，行街番工中間抽到半個鐘出來就邊度都有得剪<br />\n我柒唔柒我無咩資格講，但我又真係想睇下你個頭又有乜咁令你自豪</blockquote><br />\n三個月剪兩次有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實男仔短髮係1個月剪一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲要求高，要keep住個型，3個星期剪1次"},{"pid":"17d341713caeea25562c8c2677c95be58deb2edc","tid":376530,"uid":55256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇樣同髮型嘅姐，可能我生得柒，去QB剪完其他人都話好睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去髮型屋同qb剪完一鳩樣<br />\n比成兩舊水只係洗多個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15652630066e3cb9c2825466fbc4c260d3d02ed0","tid":376530,"uid":27289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"阿豬阿狗都學人收兩舊呢下弊呢"},{"pid":"c2d47440b799e251ec0a97f2e7cabaf54a48bfdc","tid":376530,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"我40幾蚊剪完已經好正<br />\n唔明啲人做乜要比幾舊水去剪"},{"pid":"1c7e17b4c16f7d6d740abdf4f94271490c34f5af","tid":376530,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"依家剪頭髮真係睇彩數 就算長時間揾同一個人剪都要睇佢心情"},{"pid":"ca0a599b8bca0c48bd7d32c7d1bab24db0642dab","tid":376530,"uid":85163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:10:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd7fede2df6450ada7a60ec1deeaa8ecbbebdc23","tid":376530,"uid":52490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:15:42.000Z","msg":"想睇下樓主個頭有幾型"},{"pid":"ded177037c665688d4ed3e4cec024b2861b22303","tid":376530,"uid":41080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"剪左兩年qbhouse<br />\n利申：靚仔"},{"pid":"ddd06f156b35315f51fc4fb3d971d4931185141b","tid":376530,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"自己剪"},{"pid":"4e062f5cd8ea6fca96839b9bd3197f1c91b04b95","tid":376530,"uid":136531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己剪</blockquote><br />\n我自己剪左成年了 完全唔覺同出面百幾嘅有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係間唔中撻Q就柒一陣 不過起碼係自己剪柒唔洗怨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcdc800